sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant QC as QuizController
    participant U as User
    participant Q as Question
    participant A as Achievement

    B->>QC: GET /quiz/result
    Note over QC: Redirects to /quiz/start<br>if no active quiz in session
    QC->>U: addXp(playerId, xp)
    QC->>Q: completeSession(quizId, score, xp)
    QC->>A: award(playerId)
    A-->>QC: return unlocked achievements
    Note over QC: Renders result view,<br>löscht $_SESSION['quiz']
    QC-->>B: Result View